cc:Work.dc:title: Summer: Suikawari
cc:Work.dc:description: So I know summer is almost done and gone, but I was walking home the other day and I saw a hand drawn picture for this event. I thought, if they can draw something for an official event then I can draw one just like it and put it on openclipart to share this bit of culture! I'm not the best artist, but this should depict "suikawari" which is like how they play with pinatas in the land of the raising sun. Blindfold someone and then they try to smash the watermelon! Kind of traditional, but a whole lot of fun.
